conversation_history.content: i am sad because i-95 has horrible traffic and i need to get home to my sister's bday party

I understand that dealing with traffic can be frustrating. This situation might involve the cognitive distortion of catastrophizing, where you are assuming the worst outcome because of the traffic delay. Challenge this thought by considering alternative routes or adjusting your estimated arrival time for the party based on current traffic conditions.
If you feel overwhelmed or unable to cope with these feelings, it may be helpful to seek support from a mental health professional. Remember, it's okay to reach out for help when needed.
